Text.SourceString: Howdy there, new in these waters, are ya? Welcome, sweetheart!
Text.LocalizedString: Howdy there, new in these waters, are ya? Welcome, sweetheart!

Text.SourceString: Is there anything I can help you find today?
Text.LocalizedString: Is there anything I can help you find today?

Text.SourceString: If you're lookin' for something to spice up your garden, try some marinip. Grows in all colors of the coral.
Text.LocalizedString: If you're lookin' for something to spice up your garden, try some marinip. Grows in all colors of the coral.

Text.SourceString: Well, bless my fins, isn't it a fine tide today?
Text.LocalizedString: Well, bless my fins, isn't it a fine tide today?

Text.SourceString: Goldglows, now they're a treat! They glow brighter as the night gets darker. Nature's own little lanterns.
Text.LocalizedString: Goldglows, now they're a treat! They glow brighter as the night gets darker. Nature's own little lanterns.

Text.SourceString: Oh, I'm planning a little get-together at our store for <NPCName>Todi</>, invited some of his friends from the bar.//Nothing fancy, just some good company and sea berry pie.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, I'm planning a little get-together at our store for <NPCName>Todi</>, invited some of his friends from the bar.//Nothing fancy, just some good company and sea berry pie.

Text.SourceString: We had a fresh garden in front of our store before, but it attracted a lot of wild critters to the produce, so we removed it.
Text.LocalizedString: We had a fresh garden in front of our store before, but it attracted a lot of wild critters to the produce, so we removed it.

Text.SourceString: What if we had a little corner for handmade crafts? It'd be a real nice way for the local folks to show off their talents.//<portrait=normal>Galoong could even sell his knick-knacks and whatnot.
Text.LocalizedString: What if we had a little corner for handmade crafts? It'd be a real nice way for the local folks to show off their talents.//<portrait=normal>Galoong could even sell his knick-knacks and whatnot.

Text.SourceString: Todi and I are brainstormin' some new ideas for the store. Maybe bring in some exotic sea spices. Excitin', ain't it?
Text.LocalizedString: Todi and I are brainstormin' some new ideas for the store. Maybe bring in some exotic sea spices. Excitin', ain't it?

Text.SourceString: Y'all ever need a chat or some advice, my door's always open. And I always got a fresh pot of kelp tea ready.
Text.LocalizedString: Y'all ever need a chat or some advice, my door's always open. And I always got a fresh pot of kelp tea ready.

Text.SourceString: If your sea spud's turnin' a bit pale, try singin' to it. Sounds silly, but plants do love a bit of tender care.
Text.LocalizedString: If your sea spud's turnin' a bit pale, try singin' to it. Sounds silly, but plants do love a bit of tender care.

Text.SourceString: Todi's been workin' on a new display for the store. He's got a knack for makin' things look pretty.
Text.LocalizedString: Todi's been workin' on a new display for the store. He's got a knack for makin' things look pretty.

Text.SourceString: The smell of fresh seaweed in the mornin' – now that's a blessin'.
Text.LocalizedString: The smell of fresh seaweed in the mornin' – now that's a blessin'.

Text.SourceString: Swimmin' around, <PlayerName>$player</>? That's a blessin'...That's a blessin'.
Text.LocalizedString: Swimmin' around, <PlayerName>$player</>? That's a blessin'...That's a blessin'.

Text.SourceString: Seein' a landdweller in my lifetime, down here in these waters – let me tell ya, never in my wildest dreams did I think it'd happen. That's a blessin.
Text.LocalizedString: Seein' a landdweller in my lifetime, down here in these waters – let me tell ya, never in my wildest dreams did I think it'd happen. That's a blessin.

Text.SourceString: You got yourself a place up on dry land, do ya? Well, that's a blessin', honey, a true blessin'.
Text.LocalizedString: You got yourself a place up on dry land, do ya? Well, that's a blessin', honey, a true blessin'.

Text.SourceString: Just unpacked a crate of the brightest sea grapes you ever did see. They'll be the talk of the kingdom!
Text.LocalizedString: Just unpacked a crate of the brightest sea grapes you ever did see. They'll be the talk of the kingdom!

Text.SourceString: Had to reorder them kelps twice this week – they're flyin' off the shelves!
Text.LocalizedString: Had to reorder them kelps twice this week – they're flyin' off the shelves!

Text.SourceString: Back for another batch of our sea spud crops? Let me grab the finest one for ya.
Text.LocalizedString: Back for another batch of our sea spud crops? Let me grab the finest one for ya.

Text.SourceString: These tides today are perfect for a leisurely swim. Makes the heart light, don't it?
Text.LocalizedString: These tides today are perfect for a leisurely swim. Makes the heart light, don't it?

Text.SourceString: Stormy currents like these stir up the sea something fierce. Better check your gardens for any stray kelp.
Text.LocalizedString: Stormy currents like these stir up the sea something fierce. Better check your gardens for any stray kelp.

Text.SourceString: Such clear waters today, you can see right down to the ocean floor. Makes pickin' the best crops a breeze.
Text.LocalizedString: Such clear waters today, you can see right down to the ocean floor. Makes pickin' the best crops a breeze.

Text.SourceString: There's talk of a new reef being formed near the Eastern Current. Might be a sight worth seein'.
Text.LocalizedString: There's talk of a new reef being formed near the Eastern Current. Might be a sight worth seein'.

Text.SourceString: Todi's been tinkering with a new recipe for sea jam. Says it's gonna be a game changer.
Text.LocalizedString: Todi's been tinkering with a new recipe for sea jam. Says it's gonna be a game changer.

Text.SourceString: We're seein' more sea butterflies this year. Good sign the water's stayin' clean and healthy.
Text.LocalizedString: We're seein' more sea butterflies this year. Good sign the water's stayin' clean and healthy.

Text.SourceString: Noticed the coral's been extra colorful lately. Must be all the care we've been puttin' into the reefs.
Text.LocalizedString: Noticed the coral's been extra colorful lately. Must be all the care we've been puttin' into the reefs.

Text.SourceString: Can't believe migration season's already here.//<portrait=normal>There's a whole bunch of fish swimmin' around that I don't even recognize.
Text.LocalizedString: Can't believe migration season's already here.//<portrait=normal>There's a whole bunch of fish swimmin' around that I don't even recognize.

Text.SourceString: The nights are gettin' a bit chillier. Time to stock up on some warm seaweed blankets.
Text.LocalizedString: The nights are gettin' a bit chillier. Time to stock up on some warm seaweed blankets.

Text.SourceString: You might notice a change in the tide 'round these parts, but funnily enough, it don't seem to affect the crops none.//<portrait=happy>They just keep growin' all year round.
Text.LocalizedString: You might notice a change in the tide 'round these parts, but funnily enough, it don't seem to affect the crops none.//<portrait=happy>They just keep growin' all year round.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes, just floatin' here, watchin' the fish swim by, I think about how lucky we are to call this place home.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes, just floatin' here, watchin' the fish swim by, I think about how lucky we are to call this place home.

Text.SourceString: Every mornin', I take a moment to just breathe in that salty sea water. Reminds me to be grateful for each new day.
Text.LocalizedString: Every mornin', I take a moment to just breathe in that salty sea water. Reminds me to be grateful for each new day.

Text.SourceString: There's a kind of magic in watchin' the sun rise from beneath them waves. Sure does make you appreciate the simple joys of life.
Text.LocalizedString: There's a kind of magic in watchin' the sun rise from beneath them waves. Sure does make you appreciate the simple joys of life.

Text.SourceString: Etna's garden is just flourishin'! You should see the marinethron bloomin' – all from our little store.
Text.LocalizedString: Etna's garden is just flourishin'! You should see the marinethron bloomin' – all from our little store.

Text.SourceString: Every time I swim by <NPCName>Etna</>'s place, her garden just makes my day. She's got such a knack for growin' things.
Text.LocalizedString: Every time I swim by <NPCName>Etna</>'s place, her garden just makes my day. She's got such a knack for growin' things.

Text.SourceString: Was chattin' with <NPCName>Etna</> recently, and she's as happy as a clam with her garden.//<portrait=normal>All our sea veggies and flowers, lookin' mighty fine.
Text.LocalizedString: Was chattin' with <NPCName>Etna</> recently, and she's as happy as a clam with her garden.//<portrait=normal>All our sea veggies and flowers, lookin' mighty fine.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Jannu</>'s garden started out no bigger than a sand dollar. Now, it's a sight to behold!//Our store's plants are just thrivin' under his care.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Jannu</>'s garden started out no bigger than a sand dollar. Now, it's a sight to behold!//Our store's plants are just thrivin' under his care.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Etna</> says her garden's drawin' all sorts of critters. Well, if I'm bein' honest, I don't rightly know what advice to give her.//I don't have a garden myself, you see.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Etna</> says her garden's drawin' all sorts of critters. Well, if I'm bein' honest, I don't rightly know what advice to give her.//I don't have a garden myself, you see.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes I just float by Sleepy Eel to admire the garden. I sure do like what they've done with it.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes I just float by Sleepy Eel to admire the garden. I sure do like what they've done with it.

Text.SourceString: We got ourselves a heap of crops ready for plantin'.//<portrait=happy>Now, don't you fret none 'bout us runnin' out, okay? If you need a lot, get them while they're fresh.
Text.LocalizedString: We got ourselves a heap of crops ready for plantin'.//<portrait=happy>Now, don't you fret none 'bout us runnin' out, okay? If you need a lot, get them while they're fresh.

Text.SourceString: Puttin' some music in the store ain't a half-bad idea, I tell ya. Makes the place more homey.//Fish just swim around, takin' their sweet time. They end up spendin' a bit more.
Text.LocalizedString: Puttin' some music in the store ain't a half-bad idea, I tell ya. Makes the place more homey.//Fish just swim around, takin' their sweet time. They end up spendin' a bit more.

Text.SourceString: We're not too worried about the produce outside. Nope!//In here, if you're needin' somethin' so bad you gotta take it, well then, help yourself. We got plenty to spare.
Text.LocalizedString: We're not too worried about the produce outside. Nope!//In here, if you're needin' somethin' so bad you gotta take it, well then, help yourself. We got plenty to spare.

Text.SourceString: Well, ain't it somethin' seein' a land dweller like yourself 'round these parts?//<portrait=happy>You're adaptin' quite well to the underwater life, I must say.
Text.LocalizedString: Well, ain't it somethin' seein' a land dweller like yourself 'round these parts?//<portrait=happy>You're adaptin' quite well to the underwater life, I must say.

Text.SourceString: Watchin' you learn about life under the sea, it's just fascinatin'.//Shows how much us merfolk and land dwellers can share with each other.
Text.LocalizedString: Watchin' you learn about life under the sea, it's just fascinatin'.//Shows how much us merfolk and land dwellers can share with each other.

Text.SourceString: You bring a whole new perspective to our little community. It's refreshin' to have someone from the land among us, learnin' and explorin'.
Text.LocalizedString: You bring a whole new perspective to our little community. It's refreshin' to have someone from the land among us, learnin' and explorin'.

Text.SourceString: I heard you've been lendin' a hand all over the kingdom. It's not every day we see a land-dweller takin' to our ways so kindly.
Text.LocalizedString: I heard you've been lendin' a hand all over the kingdom. It's not every day we see a land-dweller takin' to our ways so kindly.
